Release Metrics Definitions
------------------

Release Output
==============

+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| Metric                                 | Definition                             |
+========================================+========================================+
| ALT+UP                                 | OPTION+UP                              |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+DOWN                               | OPTION+DOWN                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+SHIFT+UP                           | OPTION+SHIFT+UP                        |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+SHIFT+DOWN                         | OPTION+SHIFT+DOWN                      |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+K                                 | CMD+K                                  |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+K                           | CMD+SHIFT+K                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+A                           | CMD+SHIFT+A                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+M                           | CMD+SHIFT+M                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+L                           | CMD+SHIFT+L                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+

