Release Heartbeat
=================

+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| Metric                                 | Definition                             |
+========================================+========================================+
| Time updated to RC1 (PST)                                | Date/time RC1 was cut. Check Release Discussion channel history to see when RC1 was cut.                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+DOWN                               | OPTION+DOWN                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+SHIFT+UP                           | OPTION+SHIFT+UP                        |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| ALT+SHIFT+DOWN                         | OPTION+SHIFT+DOWN                      |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+K                                 | CMD+K                                  |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+K                           | CMD+SHIFT+K                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| CTRL+SHIFT+A                           | CMD+SHIFT+A                            |
+----------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
